### Test 1: Try to create a room as a normal User (Should return 403 Forbidden)
POST {{host}}/api/admin/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Yoga Studio",
  "capacity": 15
}

### Test 2: Try to create a room as an Admin (Should return 200 OK)
POST {{host}}/api/admin/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Yoga Studio",
  "capacity": 15
}